comments: Horford (BOS) cleanly dislodges the pass in the lane from Harkless (POR).
LAR shows Harkless (POR) maintains legal guarding position while Tatum (BOS) trips on his own at the start of his dribble.
There is no conclusive angle that shows if Harkless (POR) makes contact with Horford's (BOS) arm during the driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Irving (BOS) and absorbs contact.
RLB shows Horford (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lillard (POR) and absorbs contact from Lillard's extended off-arm.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact to Smart (BOS) during the rebound.
Horford (BOS) engages with Nurkic (POR) during the inbound but does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
RLB shows Horford (BOS) cleanly dislodges the ball at the end of Lillard's (POR) drive.
[Observable in enhanced video] RLB shows Lillard (POR) steps out of bounds before releasing the pass.
LAR shows McCollum (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Smart (BOS).
Horford (BOS) delivers some contact to Lillard (POR) during the screen but does not affect his ability to defend.
McCollum (POR) makes contact to the arm of Smart (BOS) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Brown (BOS) reaches in and makes contact with Lillard's (POR) leg that affects his SQBR.
Horford (BOS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Aminu (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Irving (BOS).
Irving (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position on Lillard (POR).
